652
00:54:12,832 --> 00:54:14,166
Please try not to move.

653
00:54:31,017 --> 00:54:33,018
Focus your eyes at the ceiling, okay?

654
00:54:34,813 --> 00:54:38,065
Stay relaxed.
Stay still, that's important.

655
00:54:39,192 --> 00:54:40,984
