1101
01:31:09,588 --> 01:31:10,839
Jane, Jane.

1102
01:31:11,424 --> 01:31:14,009
Jane, look at me. It's me.

1103
01:31:25,980 --> 01:31:27,272
Shh, shh.

1104
01:31:33,571 --> 01:31:34,612
Jane.

1105
01:31:34,739 --> 01:31:35,780
